<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>The Studio // Sandbox Utilities</title>
    </head>
    <body class="bg-panel text-ink antialiased">
        <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-16 pt-16 sm:pt-24">
            <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-coral">
                Selected Work
            </p>

            <div
                class="mt-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-baseline md:justify-between gap-2 border-b border-line pb-6"
            >
                <h1
                    class="font-display text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl text-ink"
                >
                    What I've Been Building
                </h1>
                <p class="font-mono text-xs text-ink-soft">
                    By <span class="text-ink font-medium">Bljeona</span> — Independent
                    Tools
                </p>
            </div>
            <div
                class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start"
            >
                <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
                    <div>
                        <span
                            class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest bg-coral/10 text-coral px-2 py-0.5 rounded-sm font-semibold"
                        >
                            Featured App
                        </span>
                        <h3
                            class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-semibold text-ink tracking-tight"
                        >
                            <a
                                href="https://www.shareglimpse.com"
                                target="_blank"
                                class="hover:text-coral transition-colors duration-200"
                            >
                                Glimpse <span
                                    class="font-sans text-xl font-normal text-ink-soft/60"
                                    >/ shareglimpse.com</span
                                >
                            </a>
                        </h3>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="space-y-6 font-body text-base md:text-lg text-ink-soft leading-relaxed"
                    >
                        <p class="text-ink font-medium text-lg leading-snug">
                            Glimpse is a high-performance progressive web app
                            built to eliminate the friction of real-time event
                            photo sharing without sacrificing media quality or
                            user security.
                        </p>

                        <p class="text-base text-ink-soft">
                            Traditional media sharing relies on cluttered group
                            chats that aggressively crush image compression, or
                            native platforms requiring forced app downloads and
                            registration. Glimpse completely bypasses this:
                            guests scan a localized event QR code, authenticate
                            via a temporary PIN, and instantly stream
                            high-fidelity assets directly from their mobile
                            browsers.
                        </p>

                        <div
                            class="relative aspect-[16/10] bg-panel border border-line rounded-sm overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4 my-6 group bg-white"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="absolute inset-0 bg-ink/[0.01] transition-opacity group-hover:opacity-0"
                            >
                            </div>
                            <img
                                src="/glimpse.png"
                                alt="Glimpse PWA Web Interface Event Gallery Overview"
                                class="w-[92%] max-h-[92%] object-contain shadow-md rounded-sm border border-line transform rotate-1 group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-[1.02] transition-all duration-300"
                            />
                        </div>

                        <div class="pt-4 border-t border-line space-y-2">
                            <h4
                                class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-coral font-semibold"
                            >
                                Zero-Trust Public Ingestion
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-sm text-ink-soft">
                                To enable a completely frictionless onboarding
                                experience safely, the application operates on a
                                zero-trust architecture. Asynchronous background
                                workers route every incoming upload through
                                real-time computer vision models, intercepting
                                malicious or explicit payloads instantly before
                                they ever hit the hosts' live broadcast
                                slideshows or cloud storage.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-8 space-y-6">
                    <div
                        class="bg-panel border border-line p-6 rounded-sm space-y-5"
                    >
                        <h4
                            class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-ink border-b border-line pb-2 font-semibold"
                        >
                            System Blueprint
                        </h4>

                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span
                                class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-soft"
                                >Core Engine</span
                            >
                            <p class="font-body text-sm text-ink font-medium">
                                Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind
                                CSS
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span
                                class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-soft"
                                >Data & Infrastructure</span
                            >
                            <p class="font-body text-sm text-ink font-medium">
                                Supabase (Realtime Sync, PostgreSQL, Auth)
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span
                                class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-soft"
                                >Media Processing</span
                            >
                            <p class="font-body text-sm text-ink font-medium">
                                Cloudinary CDN (On-the-fly compression)
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span
                                class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-soft"
                                >AI Guardrails</span
                            >
                            <p class="font-body text-sm text-ink font-medium">
                                Google Cloud Vision AI (Asynchronous moderation)
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-1">
                            <span
                                class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-soft"
                                >Monetization</span
                            >
                            <p class="font-body text-sm text-ink font-medium">
                                Stripe API (Free Tier & Pro Plans)
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pl-1 font-mono text-xs"
                    >
                        <a
                            href="https://www.shareglimpse.com"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="text-coral font-medium hover:underline"
                        >
                            Launch App &rarr;
                        </a>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="border border-line rounded-sm overflow-hidden bg-panel/30"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-2.5 border-b border-line bg-ink/[0.02]"
                        >
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                                <span
                                    class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full border border-line bg-coral/20"
                                ></span>
                                <span
                                    class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full border border-line bg-ink-soft/10"
                                ></span>
                            </div>
                            <span
                                class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-ink-soft select-none"
                                >sandbox_dilemma.md</span
                            >
                        </div>

                        <div class="p-5 space-y-3">
                            <h5
                                class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-coral font-semibold flex items-center gap-1.5"
                            >
                                The Solo Dev Dilemma
                            </h5>
                            <p
                                class="font-sans text-xs text-ink-soft leading-relaxed"
                            >
                                If there’s one thing a solo developer hates,
                                it’s testing their own finished product. The
                                core infrastructure is solid and Stripe is live,
                                but I need fresh eyes to find the blind spots.
                            </p>
                            <p
                                class="font-sans text-xs text-ink leading-normal pt-1"
                            >
                                If you have a second, spin up a dummy event,
                                upload a few files, and <span
                                    class="text-coral font-semibold"
                                    >help me break it</span
                                > before I call it officially done. Let me know how
                                it went!
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </body>
</html>
